data.name: Installer_AppConfig_Description
data.value: To avoid an error on the initial load of our rocking Media Gallery, a simple flag was added to the /media app.config file. SUEETIE.InstallGSP = 1, which triggers Gallery Server Pro's installation wizard. Remember to change the app.config SUEETIE.InstallGSP property to "0" when you complete this wizard. If you are seeing this installation wizard for the second time, this is why.

data.name: Installer_AppConfig_Title
data.value: Attention Sueetie Listeners!

data.name: Installer_AppConfig_Description_End
data.value: Stop what you're doing to update the /[mediafolder]/app.config file by changing the SUEETIE.InstallGSP property to "0" to signify that you installed the Media Gallery. Also touch the web.config while you're at it to make sure the new app.config SUEETIE.InstallGSP property takes affect. Then click on the "Go to Media Gallery" link and enjoy your most excellent Media Gallery.
